									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thank-you once again Bhikkhu.<br>
I appreciate your clarification of the distinction between how (for most of us) ŌĆśbehaviour appearsŌĆÖ in experience and that ŌĆśappearance behavesŌĆÖ ŌĆō but that (for one who sees) ŌĆśbehaviour behavesŌĆÖ and ŌĆśappearance appearsŌĆÖ.<br>
I suspect that this is very profound and important and is something I need to incorporate more into my life.<br>
Regards,<br>
Acha</p>
